N.Z.’s Mighty River Powerto Invest NZ$466 Million in New Plant

-- B y   T r a c y   W i t h e r s
-- 
2011-06-07T20:40:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-07/n-z-s-mighty-river-powerto-invest-nz-466-million-in-new-plant.html
Mighty River Power Ltd. will invest
NZ$466 million in a new geothermal power plant at Ngatamariki
north of Taupo on  New Zealand ’s  North Island .  Consruction of the plant, which will initally generate 82
megawatts of electricity, will begin next month, the Auckland-
based company said in an e-mailed statement. The company has
secured NZ$250 million of debt to finance the project, it said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tracy Withers at 
 twithers@bloomberg.net  